A Korean fast food chain offering popular Korean street food. Available also in some MTR stations.
simple food and taste not bad

1. Food quality: Delicious but overpriced & Miso soup was bland
2. Staff Service: slow & no smile to customers. They do laugh when taking amongst staff.
3. Food ready to be taken: slow
4. Ambience: zero
5. Temperature: Freezing
6. Environmental: Not friendly. Food served by paper box and disposable utensils. Staff even gave me two sets even I was on my own.

     Additionally, no one would notify you when the food was ready to collect and drinks were self-service and no menu was ready for you to order. You have to find yourself in the counter.
